= Electron configuration =

i.e. filling the orbitals starting from 1s..... Aufbau principle unpaired and paired electrons Hund's rule: 1 e- in each orbital before pairing in p orbitals shorthand: <math> 1s^2\ 2s^2\ 2p^2</math> etc.

